BRICHANT, Appellant, v. BRONWER et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Arthur Brichant against George H. Brouwer and others.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and FOLLETT, J.

A. Gruber, for appellant. Carter, Lindon & Van Schaick, for respondents.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
